---
description: Python standards for VoxMesh AI services
globs:
  - "services/ai/**"
  - "**/*.py"
---

- Python version pinned per service (`requires-python` + `constraints.txt`); currently 3.12–3.14.
- FastAPI for management/batch APIs; gRPC for streaming audio and high-throughput paths.
- `ruff` and `mypy` must pass; pytest for tests.
- Model access only through the provider interfaces (STT, translation, diarization,
  summarization, embeddings, vector store) — never import a vendor SDK in business logic and
  never hard-code a model name outside provider configuration.
- Record model provider + version on every produced artifact (transcripts, translations,
  summaries, embeddings).
- Vector records carry tenant ID, source segment/chapter ID, embedding model + version +
  dimensions, language, ACL metadata, timestamps (master prompt §17).
